---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Services"
  description="WordPress sur mesure, développement Next.js/Astro et maintenance de sites web. Devis gratuit sous 48h avec un développeur indépendant."
>
  <section class="pt-28 pb-20 sm:pb-28 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div
        class="border border-vert/20 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-sm"
      >
        <!-- Terminal title bar -->
        <div
          class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 sm:px-5 py-3 border-b border-vert/10 bg-[#F8F8F6]"
        >
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f56]"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ffbd2e]"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#28c840]"></span>
          <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-[#2d2a24]/70 font-medium"
            >olivier@otvt:~/services</span
          >
        </div>
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="px-6 sm:px-12 py-8 sm:py-14">
          <p
            class="text-xs text-vert/85 font-mono mb-8 sm:mb-10 leading-relaxed"
          >
            <span class="text-vert font-semibold">olivier@otvt</span>:<span
              class="text-jaune">~</span
            ><span class="text-[#2d2a24]/70">$ </span><span
              class="text-[#2d2a24]/70">cat services.txt</span
            >
          </p>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-12 sm:gap-16">
            <div class="sm:col-span-1">
              <p
                class="text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.15em] text-vert/85 uppercase"
              >
                Services
              </p>
              <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-[#2d2a24]">
                Ce que je propose
              </h1>
              <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[#2d2a24]/70 leading-relaxed">
                Du site vitrine à l'application complexe, chaque projet est
                unique.
              </p>
              <a
                href="/contact"
                class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-vert text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-vert/90 transition-all duration-200"
              >
                Démarrer
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  width="14"
                  height="14"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  ><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"
                  ></path></svg
                >
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="sm:col-span-2 space-y-10">
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#2d2a24]">WordPress</h2>
                <p
                  class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#2d2a24]/70 leading-relaxed max-w-lg"
                >
                  Thème sur mesure, WooCommerce, plugins. Je construis chaque
                  site depuis zéro, pas de template pré-fait. Design sur mesure,
                  performance optimisée.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Thème sur mesure</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >WooCommerce</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Performance</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#2d2a24]">
                  Développement sur mesure
                </h2>
                <p
                  class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#2d2a24]/70 leading-relaxed max-w-lg"
                >
                  Next.js, Astro, React, Node.js. Des sites ultra-rapides aux
                  applications dynamiques. Stack moderne, déploiement continu.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Next.js / Astro</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >React / TypeScript</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Vercel</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#2d2a24]">
                  Maintenance & Évolution
                </h2>
                <p
                  class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#2d2a24]/70 leading-relaxed max-w-lg"
                >
                  Audit technique, mises à jour de sécurité, amélioration des
                  performances. Je reprends aussi des sites existants pour les
                  moderniser.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Audit & Sécurité</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Migration</span
                  >
                  <span
                    class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
                    >Performance</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section class="pb-20 sm:pb-28 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div
        class="border border-vert/20 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-sm"
      >
        <div
          class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 sm:px-5 py-3 border-b border-vert/10 bg-[#F8F8F6]"
        >
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f56]"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ffbd2e]"></span>
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#28c840]"></span>
          <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-[#2d2a24]/70 font-medium"
            >olivier@otvt:~/methodology</span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="px-6 sm:px-12 py-8 sm:py-14">
          <p
            class="text-xs text-vert/85 font-mono mb-8 sm:mb-10 leading-relaxed"
          >
            <span class="text-vert font-semibold">olivier@otvt</span>:<span
              class="text-jaune">~</span
            ><span class="text-[#2d2a24]/70">$ </span><span
              class="text-[#2d2a24]/70">cat process.sh</span
            >
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.15em] text-vert/85 uppercase mb-6"
          >
            Méthode
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-[#2d2a24]">
            Comment je travaille
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[#2d2a24]/70 leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
            Transparence, itérations rapides et qualité. Un process simple et
            efficace.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-12 grid sm:grid-cols-4 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-vert/10 text-vert text-lg font-bold mb-4"
                >01</span
              >
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-[#2d2a24]">Découverte</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-[#2d2a24]/70 leading-relaxed">
                Analyse de vos besoins, objectifs et contraintes. Un cahier des
                charges clair pour partir sur de bonnes bases.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-jaune/20 text-[#7a5c00] text-lg font-bold mb-4"
                >02</span
              >
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-[#2d2a24]">Conception</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-[#2d2a24]/70 leading-relaxed">
                Maquettes, validation et architecture technique. Vous approuvez
                chaque étape avant le développement.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-vert/10 text-vert text-lg font-bold mb-4"
                >03</span
              >
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-[#2d2a24]">
                Développement
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-[#2d2a24]/70 leading-relaxed">
                Itérations courtes, tests continus. Vous suivez l'avancement en
                temps réel et donnez votre feedback.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <span
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-jaune/20 text-[#7a5c00] text-lg font-bold mb-4"
                >04</span
              >
              <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-[#2d2a24]">Lancement</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-[#2d2a24]/70 leading-relaxed">
                Mise en ligne, formation et suivi. Je reste disponible après la
                livraison pour assurer la tranquillité.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <!-- Backdrop overlay -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#F0EFEC] opacity-60"></div>
      <div class="relative max-w-xl mx-auto">
        <div
          class="border border-vert/25 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-white shadow-lg shadow-vert/5"
        >
          <!-- Title bar -->
          <div
            class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 sm:px-5 py-3 border-b border-vert/10 bg-[#F8F8F6]"
          >
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ff5f56]"></span>
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#ffbd2e]"></span>
            <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[#28c840]"></span>
            <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-[#2d2a24]/70 font-medium"
              >olivier@otvt:~/call</span
            >
          </div>
          <!-- Content -->
          <div class="px-6 sm:px-10 py-8 sm:py-10 text-center">
            <p class="text-xs text-vert/85 font-mono mb-6 leading-relaxed">
              <span class="text-vert font-semibold">olivier@otvt</span>:<span
                class="text-jaune">~</span
              ><span class="text-[#2d2a24]/70">$ </span><span
                class="text-[#2d2a24]/70">./call-to-action.sh</span
              >
            </p>
            <span
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-vert/10 text-vert mb-5"
            >
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="20"
                height="20"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path
                  d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"
                ></path></svg
              >
            </span>
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#2d2a24]">
              Vous ne savez pas par où commencer ?
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-[#2d2a24]/70">
              On en parle 30 minutes sans engagement.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-vert text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-vert/90 transition-all duration-200 shadow-sm"
            >
              Réserver un appel
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                width="14"
                height="14"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                fill="none"
                stroke="currentColor"
                stroke-width="2"
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                ><path d="M5 12h14"></path><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path></svg
              >
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
